text: Eunidia rufula is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fairmaire in 1905. It contains the varietas Eunidia rufula var. pauliani.BioLib.cz - Eunidia rufula. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1905
title: Eunidia rufula
